{"tid":1255972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612有去發夢野餐嘅，記得仲要出嚟","createTime":"2019-06-24T18:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T01:30:54.000Z","uid":20058,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae115f8ed90608d3ad30024149349e01724c647","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"唔好因為個目標偏離左唔係撤回<br />\n就會放鬆<br />\n我身邊有幾個就已經因爲咁<br />\n決定唔再參加<br />\n唔好唔記得612係一場「暴動」<br />\n無論你嗰日係前線都有好物資站又好<br />\n救護員都好<br />\n總之你做乜撚嘢<br />\n你都係會入暴動罪<br />\n衰啲講句，只要你嗰日喺金鐘中環你已經係「暴動」<br />\n等呢件事過返幾個月<br />\n班狗就會開始做嘢<br />\n大家見識到班狗未食藥已經係乜樣<br />\n嗰日612根據毅進制就話有四萬人參與<br />\n實際上有幾多大家都知啦<br />\n到時一定有殺錯無放過<br />\n為自己<br />\n一定要繼續爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9839e31825a51aff44c75df97ea28fae8741060a","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426de27e696ab1adb7ca87b4be18fc02d3977df4","tid":1255972,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c831b8850f945c3219e8c82e610476a25e1ff5c","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426de27e696ab1adb7ca87b4be18fc02d3977df4","tid":1255972,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"就算冇都非法集結啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你清白<br />\n佢都未必咁容易放過你<br />\n起碼搞足一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b83b39b8a0f0109f8b5d328b16810d9c0c519","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"可能我有啲嘢都係誇大<br />\n總之大家小心<br />\n唔好以為冇埞野就安全"},{"pid":"f5314d5ec852836280d0f2c5fa3e77cd855a4378","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426de27e696ab1adb7ca87b4be18fc02d3977df4","tid":1255972,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"Btw記得有巴打講過<br />\n只要你可以喺後邊要叫支持又或者其他嘢就已經可以入你暴動罪"},{"pid":"5217f5fbbd953e911aa20501daf90eb9d27d1b26","tid":1255972,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c831b8850f945c3219e8c82e610476a25e1ff5c","tid":1255972,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"426de27e696ab1adb7ca87b4be18fc02d3977df4","tid":1255972,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"就算冇都非法集結啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算你清白<br />\n佢都未必咁容易放過你<br />\n起碼搞足一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"ys<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之有構成公眾不安就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候自組九龍城獨立泛民主派助選團<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1255719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1255719</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ac33652f550a2eae56713aae0988eaa4b79860d","tid":1255972,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:33:02.000Z","msg":"爸爸媽媽 我哋有啲嘢想講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dauArS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dauArS</a><br />\